    <item>
      <title>Lutnick 就 5000 万美元 Newmark 奖金达成和解，让他继续保留这笔奖金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/lutnick-settlement-on-50-million-newmark-bonus-lets-him-keep-it</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据法庭文件显示，Cantor Fitzgerald LP 首席执行官 Howard Lutnick 与投资者就 5000 万美元奖金达成和解，因此他可以保住这笔钱，而该公司的 Newmark Group Inc. 将通过保险获得赔付。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/lutnick-settlement-on-50-million-newmark-bonus-lets-him-keep-it</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 13:02:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
